            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1620148944,
            "creation_date": 1620148944,
            "body": "<p>You can encode/stringify push the data, while pulling data you can decode/parse the data.<\/p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Encode -&gt; Decode<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Stringify -&gt; Parse<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n",
            "answer_id": 67389358,
